  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to evaluate the effectiveness and safety of cNEP (continuous
      negative external pressure) for the treatment of obstructive sleep apnea during two weeks of
      home use in subjects of Japanese ethnicity.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
