  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  both parents ethnically Japanese, or one parent Japanese and the other east-Asian

          -  PSG (polysomnogram) done within the previous 12 months that shows an AHI of 10-50/hr
             and &lt;80% of apneas and hypopneas are obstructive

          -  cNEP collar fits and is well-tolerated

        Key exclusion Criteria:

          -  BMI &gt;34

          -  abnormalities in neck structure

          -  sleep disturbance other than obstructive sleep apnea

          -  serious medical illness

          -  pregnancy
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
